div.p:
A draft text of a letter to be addressed on this subject to the
                        Secretary-General of the United Nations was agreed
                        for submission to the Council. (Annex 2)

p.note:
This article was amended and adopted by the
                                Council of Foreign Ministers at its 17th Meeting, December 6, 1946;
                                see the Record of Decisions of that Council meeting, p. 1462.
